    <title>在jsp页面使用C标签c:forEach显示List</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2020/11/29/test2/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2020/11/29/test2/</id>
    <published>2020-11-29T15:16:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-11-29T15:49:46.826Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="起因"><a href="#起因" class="headerlink" title="起因"></a>起因</h1><p>​    这两天在使用这个c标签中出现了一些问题，耗费了大量时间，特此记录。</p><p>  首先，我们在使用这个标签时，需要先熟悉它的基本使用规则。</p><blockquote><p>&lt;c:forEach var=”name” items=”Collection” varStatus=”statusName” begin=”begin” end=”end” step=”step”&gt;</c:forEach></p></blockquote><p>items:你需要遍历的集合的名称</p><p>var:自己取名,是集合中的一个元素</p><p>varStatus:表示集合中每个元素的相关信息,有4种状态:index(所在位置，即索引).count(总共已迭代的次数).first(是否为第一个位置),last(是否为最后一个位置)</p><p>begin:从第几个元素开始</p><p>end:从第几个元素结束</p><p>step:是一个一个循环还是跳跃着循环.</p><h1 id="实例"><a href="#实例" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h1><p>   在SpringMVC+Mybatis下通过Controller发送一个List至Jsp页面,通过C:forEach循环显示</p><p>首先新建一个关于用户的实体类</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@getter</span> <span class="meta">@setter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">UserTable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> id;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">private</span> String password;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">private</span> String name;</span><br><span class="line">  ....</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着新建一个List,并向其中存入用户的数据</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> List&lt;UserTable&gt; <span class="title">show</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">List&lt;UserTable&gt;  list=<span class="keyword">new</span> ArrayList&lt;UserTable&gt;();      </span><br><span class="line">    UserTable re1=<span class="keyword">new</span> UserTable();  </span><br><span class="line">    re1.setId(<span class="number">111</span>);  </span><br><span class="line">    re1.setName(<span class="string">&quot;wp&quot;</span>);  </span><br><span class="line">    re1.setPassword(<span class="string">&quot;1111&quot;</span>);  </span><br><span class="line">       UserTable re2=<span class="keyword">new</span> UserTable();  </span><br><span class="line">    re2.setId(<span class="number">222</span>);  </span><br><span class="line">    re2.setName(<span class="string">&quot;qs&quot;</span>);  </span><br><span class="line">    re2.setPassword(<span class="string">&quot;2222&quot;</span>);  </span><br><span class="line">    list.add(re1); </span><br><span class="line">       list.add(re2);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> list;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着在Controller中向Jsp页面发送这个数据</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">List&lt;UserTable&gt; info=showDao.show();</span><br><span class="line">model.addAttribute(<span class="string">&quot;info&quot;</span>,info);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;success&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在Jsp中接收该数据,须在Jsp页面中添加该路径,同时需要在WEB-INF中的lib中加入<strong>jstl</strong>和<strong>standard</strong>架包才能顺利使用c标签</p><blockquote><p>&lt;%@taglib uri=”<a href="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core&quot;">http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core&quot;</a> prefix=”c” %&gt;</p></blockquote><p>经过上面的配置,就可以在jsp中显示list了</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- 输出结果集 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                   &lt;c:forEach items=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;info&#125;&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">var</span>=<span class="string">&quot;t&quot;</span>&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                                 &lt;td&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">c:out</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;t.id&#125;&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span>&lt;/td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                   &lt;td&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">c:out</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;t.name&#125;&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span>&lt;/td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   &lt;td&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">c:out</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;$&#123;t.password&#125;&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span>&lt;/td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                   &lt;td <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;btns&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                                &lt;a href=<span class="string">&quot;changeview.jsp?id=$&#123;t.id&#125;&quot;</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;btn&quot;</span>&gt;修改&lt;/a&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;a href=<span class="string">&quot;deleteController?id=$&#123;t.id&#125;&quot;</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;btn&quot;</span>&gt;删除&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                            &lt;/td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">     </span><br><span class="line">                                   &lt;/tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                                  &lt;/c:forEach&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                              </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="End"><a href="#End" class="headerlink" title="End"></a>End</h1>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
